{"about_the_game":"<strong>Welcome to Grifford Academy </strong><br>Dive into the enigmatic world of Grifford Academy, a mesmerizing coming-of-age RPG where magic, monsters, and teenage turmoil collide. Join Erika, Viva, and Cap as they navigate the mystical book realm of Caldria, uncovering secrets and battling sinister forces.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445780/extras/Outfit.gif?t=1737345930\" /><br><br><i>Uncover secrets in the mystical realm of Caldria</i><br><br><strong>Immersive World-Building</strong><br>Explore the beautifully crafted realm of Caldria, filled with menacing creatures and otherworldly discoveries. Equip your squad, level up, and immerse yourself in strategic turn-based combat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445780/extras/Zoom_In_Gif.gif?t=1737345930\" /><br><br><strong>Your Choices Matter</strong><br>Guide your characters through personal challenges and watch them evolve based on your decisions. Every choice matters, influencing the story and the characters' development in unexpected ways. Engage with a unique dialogue flow that allows you to connect with the characters and their journey at your own pace.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445780/extras/Choices__Resized__.gif?t=1737345930\" /><br><br><strong>Strategic Turn-Based Combat</strong><br>Equip your squad, level up, and immerse yourself in strategic turn-based combat. Grifford Academy offers both Story Mode for a relaxed experience and Strategy Mode for those seeking a challenge. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2445780/extras/Combat.gif?t=1737345930\" /><br><br><strong>Welcome to a journey where heart meets strategy and every battle counts.</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st